@startuml
title Feature 029 / Admin PIM sequence
actor "Категорийный администратор" as CategoryAdmin
actor "PIM-менеджер" as PimManager
actor "Медиа-менеджер" as MediaManager
participant "Frontend /admin/pim" as FE
participant "Auth/RBAC context" as Auth
participant "AdminPimController" as Controller
participant "AdminPimService" as Service
database "admin-pim repository" as Repo
participant "S3/MinIO metadata" as Storage
participant "Catalog public read model" as Catalog

CategoryAdmin -> FE: открыть PIM workspace
FE -> Auth: current session + permissions
Auth --> FE: ADMIN_PIM_VIEW, ADMIN_PIM_MANAGE
FE -> Controller: GET /api/admin-pim/workspace
Controller -> Service: loadWorkspace(actor)
Service -> Repo: counts and latest audit
Repo --> Service: summary
Service --> Controller: AdminPimWorkspaceResponse + STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PIM_WORKSPACE_LOADED
Controller --> FE: 200 summary

CategoryAdmin -> FE: создать/активировать категорию face-care
FE -> Controller: POST /categories
Controller -> Service: createCategory(request, actor)
Service -> Repo: validate slug and parent tree
Repo --> Service: no conflict
Service -> Repo: save category DRAFT + audit CATEGORY_CREATED
Repo --> Service: categoryId
Service --> Controller: CategoryResponse + STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PIM_CATEGORY_SAVED
Controller --> FE: 201 category
FE -> Controller: POST /categories/{categoryId}/activate
Controller -> Service: activateCategory(categoryId, actor)
Service -> Repo: validate no cycle, active window, slug uniqueness
Service -> Repo: update ACTIVE + audit CATEGORY_ACTIVATED
Controller --> FE: 200 active category

PimManager -> FE: создать товар BOG-SERUM-001
FE -> Controller: POST /products
Controller -> Service: createProduct(request, actor)
Service -> Repo: validate unique SKU/article, active category
Repo --> Service: valid references
Service -> Repo: save product DRAFT + audit PRODUCT_CREATED
Controller --> FE: 201 product detail with validationChecklist

PimManager -> FE: попробовать опубликовать без главного изображения
FE -> Controller: POST /products/{productId}/publish
Controller -> Service: publishProduct(productId, versionComment)
Service -> Repo: load product categories/media
Repo --> Service: no MAIN_IMAGE APPROVED
Service --> Controller: validation error STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PIM_PRODUCT_MAIN_IMAGE_REQUIRED
Controller --> FE: 400 mnemonic + field mainImage

MediaManager -> FE: добавить metadata главного изображения
FE -> Controller: POST /products/{productId}/media
Controller -> Service: addMediaMetadata(productId, request, actor)
Service -> Storage: validate fileReferenceId/checksum metadata
Storage --> Service: metadata accepted
Service -> Repo: save media DRAFT + audit PRODUCT_MEDIA_CREATED
Controller --> FE: 201 media + STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PIM_MEDIA_SAVED
FE -> Controller: POST /media/{mediaId}/approve
Controller -> Service: approveMedia(mediaId, actor)
Service -> Repo: deactivate previous main image, approve media, audit PRODUCT_MEDIA_APPROVED
Controller --> FE: 200 approved media

PimManager -> FE: опубликовать товар
FE -> Controller: POST /products/{productId}/publish
Controller -> Service: publishProduct(productId, versionComment)
Service -> Repo: validate required fields, active category, approved main image
Service -> Repo: create product version, status PUBLISHED, audit PRODUCT_PUBLISHED
Service -> Catalog: publish product/category render data
Catalog --> Service: render model accepted
Controller --> FE: 200 product + STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PIM_PRODUCT_PUBLISHED

PimManager -> FE: import/export
FE -> Controller: POST /imports with Idempotency-Key
Controller -> Service: startImport(request, idempotencyKey)
Service -> Repo: find existing import by idempotencyKey
alt existing job
  Repo --> Service: existing import job
else new job
  Service -> Repo: validate rows, apply changes, audit IMPORT_JOB_APPLIED
end
Controller --> FE: 201 import job
FE -> Controller: POST /exports
Controller -> Service: createExport(filter, actor)
Service -> Repo: collect filtered catalog and checksum
Service -> Repo: save export job + audit CATALOG_EXPORTED
Controller --> FE: 201 export summary
@enduml